window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Inspector Rebus Book 7</p> <p>Struggling through another Edinburgh winter Rebus finds himself sucked into a web of intrigue that throws up more questions than answers.</p> <p>Was the Lord Provost's daughter kidnapped or just another runaway? Why is a city councillor shredding documents that should have been waste paper years ago? And why on earth is Rebus invited to a clay pigeon shoot at the home of the Scottish Office's Permanent Secretary?</p> <p>Sucked into the machine that is modern Scotland, Rebus confronts the fact that some of his enemies may be beyond justice...</p>"; 
